  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 2.0,
      "text": "Wow, good morning, Chris"
    },
    {
      "start": 2.0,
      "end": 3.76,
      "text": "Hello, Jo Sam"
    },
    {
      "start": 3.76,
      "end": 4.88,
      "text": "네, 너무 반갑습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 4.88,
      "end": 5.88,
      "text": "반갑습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 5.88,
      "end": 6.88,
      "text": "반갑습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 6.88,
      "end": 9.68,
      "text": "네, 이렇게 월요일 아침에 오늘 또 스크린 잉글리시 이어가는데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 9.68,
      "end": 12.1,
      "text": "프랑코에 대해서 말이에요."
    },
    {
      "start": 12.46,
      "end": 14.48,
      "text": "알면 알수록 프랑코는"
    },
    {
      "start": 14.48,
      "end": 17.78,
      "text": "It's not like a monster, like a fairy"
    },
    {
      "start": 17.78,
      "end": 18.86,
      "text": "A fairy?"
    },
    {
      "start": 19.04,
      "end": 19.28,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 19.28,
      "end": 20.66,
      "text": "Like the tooth fairy?"
    },
    {
      "start": 21.04,
      "end": 22.24,
      "text": "He gives you money?"
    },
    {
      "start": 22.48,
      "end": 23.48,
      "text": "He takes your teeth?"
    },
    {
      "start": 23.8,
      "end": 24.44,
      "text": "아니요, 아니요."
    },
    {
      "start": 24.58,
      "end": 27.62,
      "text": "그 singing fairy라고 표현하면 어울릴 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 27.88,
      "end": 28.98,
      "text": "노래하는 요정?"
    },
    {
      "start": 29.92,
      "end": 33.28,
      "text": "역시 우리는 이렇게 프랑코의 외모만 보고서"
    },
    {
      "start": 33.28,
      "end": 36.48,
      "text": "조지하면 안 된다라는 교훈도 얻는 것 같습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 36.48,
      "end": 40.34,
      "text": "Yeah, he has a good voice and he's adorable."
    },
    {
      "start": 40.76,
      "end": 43.86,
      "text": "Just because he looks like a giant, ugly flea"
    },
    {
      "start": 43.86,
      "end": 46.84,
      "text": "Doesn't mean you need to be scared of him."
    },
    {
      "start": 47.06,
      "end": 47.82,
      "text": "그러니까요."
    },
    {
      "start": 48.12,
      "end": 49.8,
      "text": "그러면, when you think of monsters,"
    },
    {
      "start": 50.16,
      "end": 52.0,
      "text": "who comes to your mind first?"
    },
    {
      "start": 52.18,
      "end": 52.66,
      "text": "Monsters?"
    },
    {
      "start": 53.34,
      "end": 55.46,
      "text": "Oh, some people come to mind."
    },
    {
      "start": 56.16,
      "end": 56.56,
      "text": "Ah, people?"
    },
    {
      "start": 56.9,
      "end": 57.64,
      "text": "No, I'm just kidding."
    },
    {
      "start": 58.06,
      "end": 59.66,
      "text": "Not people."
    },
    {
      "start": 60.24,
      "end": 63.14,
      "text": "Monsters, by definition, are not human beings."
    },
    {
      "start": 63.6,
      "end": 65.26,
      "text": "So, when I think of monsters,"
    },
    {
      "start": 65.26,
      "end": 68.88,
      "text": "I think of the old movies I used to watch"
    },
    {
      "start": 68.88,
      "end": 69.88,
      "text": "when I was growing up."
    },
    {
      "start": 70.0,
      "end": 71.38,
      "text": "Some monster movies."
    },
    {
      "start": 71.62,
      "end": 73.18,
      "text": "The classic monsters."
    },
    {
      "start": 73.62,
      "end": 75.96,
      "text": "좀 무서운 그런 느낌의"
    },
    {
      "start": 75.96,
      "end": 77.66,
      "text": "무비를 보셨나요, 어렸을 때?"
    },
    {
      "start": 77.88,
      "end": 79.4,
      "text": "They were a little bit creepy."
    },
    {
      "start": 79.76,
      "end": 81.06,
      "text": "Like the old black and white."
    },
    {
      "start": 81.2,
      "end": 83.34,
      "text": "My dad loved classic movies."
    },
    {
      "start": 83.64,
      "end": 85.08,
      "text": "Black and white movies."
    },
    {
      "start": 85.08,
      "end": 85.48,
      "text": "I see."
    },
    {
      "start": 85.72,
      "end": 87.3,
      "text": "And I could hookback 채널 많이 샀어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 87.68,
      "end": 88.78,
      "text": "Hookback 영화 전용 채널."
    },
    {
      "start": 88.78,
      "end": 91.2,
      "text": "And every evening,"
    },
    {
      "start": 91.3,
      "end": 92.96,
      "text": "he would watch these black and white movies."
    },
    {
      "start": 93.4,
      "end": 96.4,
      "text": "Dracula, like from the 1930s."
    },
    {
      "start": 97.04,
      "end": 99.7,
      "text": "Frankenstein, from like 100 years ago."
    },
    {
      "start": 99.8,
      "end": 101.14,
      "text": "He would watch these movies."
    },
    {
      "start": 101.4,
      "end": 104.98,
      "text": "And those were the first monsters I saw on TV."
    },
    {
      "start": 104.98,
      "end": 106.98,
      "text": "와, 추억이 방울방울합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 107.42,
      "end": 110.5,
      "text": "저도 Frankenstein, 소설로도 보고,"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.7,
      "end": 111.48,
      "text": "영화로도 보고,"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.74,
      "end": 113.6,
      "text": "그때 되게 무섭다라는 생각도 했고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 114.1,
      "end": 116.1,
      "text": "저는 우리나라 영화 중에서,"
    },
    {
      "start": 116.46,
      "end": 117.9,
      "text": "정말, it's called 괴물."
    },
    {
      "start": 118.44,
      "end": 119.64,
      "text": "Oh, 봉준호."
    },
    {
      "start": 120.04,
      "end": 123.34,
      "text": "네, 송강호 배우가 여기서 staring 했잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 123.5,
      "end": 125.06,
      "text": "네, 감독님은 봉준호고."
    },
    {
      "start": 125.1,
      "end": 125.62,
      "text": "맞아요, 맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 125.78,
      "end": 126.98,
      "text": "그래서 그 영화 속에 그 괴물이"
    },
    {
      "start": 127.64,
      "end": 130.52,
      "text": "굉장히 충격적으로 다가왔었던 기억이 납니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 130.66,
      "end": 132.48,
      "text": "I watched that, the Han River monster."
    },
    {
      "start": 132.68,
      "end": 132.98,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 132.98,
      "end": 135.42,
      "text": "He looked kind of like a tadpole,"
    },
    {
      "start": 135.7,
      "end": 138.06,
      "text": "a giant tadpole with teeth."
    },
    {
      "start": 138.3,
      "end": 139.96,
      "text": "뭔가 tadpole하고 giant하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.96,
      "end": 142.26,
      "text": "되게 뭔가 ironic 걸 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 143.4,
      "end": 144.74,
      "text": "그 몬스터의 경우는"
    },
    {
      "start": 144.74,
      "end": 146.98,
      "text": "killed so many people in that movie."
    },
    {
      "start": 147.46,
      "end": 148.94,
      "text": "정말 scary 했단 말이죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 149.14,
      "end": 151.22,
      "text": "하지만 우리 이 영화에서 보는"
    },
    {
      "start": 151.22,
      "end": 153.62,
      "text": "프랑코는 아무도 해치지 않아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 154.2,
      "end": 155.1,
      "text": "He's innocent."
    },
    {
      "start": 155.36,
      "end": 156.3,
      "text": "He's lovable."
    },
    {
      "start": 156.64,
      "end": 157.16,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 157.52,
      "end": 159.3,
      "text": "Yeah, do you like this kind of monster,"
    },
    {
      "start": 159.4,
      "end": 160.1,
      "text": "this flea monster?"
    },
    {
      "start": 160.1,
      "end": 160.84,
      "text": "아, 그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 160.98,
      "end": 162.1,
      "text": "성격도 그렇고,"
    },
    {
      "start": 162.1,
      "end": 163.92,
      "text": "점점 갈수록 되게 adorable,"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.14,
      "end": 166.36,
      "text": "lovely하다라는 생각을 하게 됐고,"
    },
    {
      "start": 166.44,
      "end": 168.92,
      "text": "사실 이런 애니메이션에서는"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.92,
      "end": 170.88,
      "text": "there are a bunch of lovely monsters,"
    },
    {
      "start": 171.46,
      "end": 172.86,
      "text": "like franco, 그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 173.16,
      "end": 175.54,
      "text": "이 프랑코 같은 사랑스러운"
    },
    {
      "start": 175.54,
      "end": 177.4,
      "text": "몬스터들이 꽤 많이 있습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 177.62,
      "end": 179.42,
      "text": "예를 들어서 몬스터 호텔"
    },
    {
      "start": 179.42,
      "end": 181.5,
      "text": "시리즈에서도 나오잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 181.5,
      "end": 183.24,
      "text": "GMP에서 한 영화 아닙니까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.74,
      "end": 185.02,
      "text": "아, 저 오기 전에."
    },
    {
      "start": 185.52,
      "end": 185.94,
      "text": "아, 예."
    },
    {
      "start": 186.42,
      "end": 188.54,
      "text": "모든 영화 우리 조 선생님 오기 전에 했나 봐요."
    },
    {
      "start": 189.12,
      "end": 190.86,
      "text": "예, 정말 수많은 영화가 걷어갔네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 190.86,
      "end": 192.38,
      "text": "trans, what is it called?"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.74,
      "end": 193.34,
      "text": "Transylvania."
    },
    {
      "start": 194.46,
      "end": 194.9,
      "text": "Transylvania."
    },
    {
      "start": 195.68,
      "end": 196.62,
      "text": "It's a series."
    },
    {
      "start": 196.86,
      "end": 199.32,
      "text": "We did the third one in the series."
    },
    {
      "start": 199.52,
      "end": 202.9,
      "text": "And there's a Dracula who runs a hotel."
    },
    {
      "start": 203.12,
      "end": 204.42,
      "text": "And he has a family."
    },
    {
      "start": 204.64,
      "end": 205.8,
      "text": "And he's adorable."
    },
    {
      "start": 206.04,
      "end": 207.38,
      "text": "He's not scary at all."
    },
    {
      "start": 207.42,
      "end": 209.14,
      "text": "He's not like the Dracula I remember"
    },
    {
      "start": 209.14,
      "end": 210.66,
      "text": "from the black and white movie,"
    },
    {
      "start": 210.74,
      "end": 212.18,
      "text": "who sucks blood."
    },
    {
      "start": 212.68,
      "end": 213.86,
      "text": "He's not scary."
    },
    {
      "start": 213.86,
      "end": 216.04,
      "text": "예, 자, 이번 프랑코도"
    },
    {
      "start": 216.04,
      "end": 217.9,
      "text": "was one of the kind 였습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 218.34,
      "end": 219.36,
      "text": "예, 그럼 오늘 장면"
    },
    {
      "start": 219.36,
      "end": 220.22,
      "text": "먼저 듣고 올까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 221.03,
      "end": 222.41,
      "text": "If only we could shrink him down"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.41,
      "end": 223.61,
      "text": "to his normal size."
    },
    {
      "start": 223.87,
      "end": 225.05,
      "text": "Then no one would ever find him."
    },
    {
      "start": 225.31,
      "end": 225.87,
      "text": "Smaller you are,"
    },
    {
      "start": 225.93,
      "end": 226.81,
      "text": "the less people look at you."
    },
    {
      "start": 227.31,
      "end": 228.79,
      "text": "At least that's been my experience."
    },
    {
      "start": 228.99,
      "end": 230.11,
      "text": "There's only one person"
    },
    {
      "start": 230.11,
      "end": 231.13,
      "text": "who could save 프랑코"
    },
    {
      "start": 231.13,
      "end": 232.55,
      "text": "and he's in New York right now."
    },
    {
      "start": 232.87,
      "end": 233.19,
      "text": "Mm-hmm."
    },
    {
      "start": 233.75,
      "end": 234.79,
      "text": "But we don't need him."
    },
    {
      "start": 235.53,
      "end": 237.39,
      "text": "Lucille, no offense."
    },
    {
      "start": 237.55,
      "end": 239.53,
      "text": "We're talking big-time science here, okay?"
    },
    {
      "start": 239.65,
      "end": 240.67,
      "text": "All I know is deliveries."
    },
    {
      "start": 240.95,
      "end": 242.15,
      "text": "Emile's all about movies."
    },
    {
      "start": 242.37,
      "end": 243.59,
      "text": "You're an expert in show business,"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.59,
      "end": 244.13,
      "text": "but, you know."
    },
    {
      "start": 244.15,
      "end": 244.63,
      "text": "Exactly."
    },
    {
      "start": 246.38,
      "end": 247.96,
      "text": "지난주에 이 서장이"
    },
    {
      "start": 247.96,
      "end": 250.4,
      "text": "violated her private room."
    },
    {
      "start": 250.9,
      "end": 252.44,
      "text": "There was no one inside."
    },
    {
      "start": 252.68,
      "end": 253.62,
      "text": "정말 다행이었죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 254.12,
      "end": 256.18,
      "text": "프랑코가 잘 숨어 있었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 256.38,
      "end": 258.14,
      "text": "Yeah, he hid really, really well."
    },
    {
      "start": 258.26,
      "end": 259.6,
      "text": "하지만 이제는"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.6,
      "end": 262.1,
      "text": "이 프랑코를 제대로 구할 방법을"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.1,
      "end": 263.1,
      "text": "찾아야 되겠죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 263.82,
      "end": 265.6,
      "text": "그래서 지금 이 친구들이"
    },
    {
      "start": 265.6,
      "end": 266.96,
      "text": "they talked about the things"
    },
    {
      "start": 266.96,
      "end": 269.78,
      "text": "that they were good at."
    },
    {
      "start": 269.84,
      "end": 270.16,
      "text": "그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 270.28,
      "end": 271.9,
      "text": "And they came up with a plan,"
    },
    {
      "start": 271.9,
      "end": 273.32,
      "text": "a special plan"
    },
    {
      "start": 273.32,
      "end": 275.16,
      "text": "to save the cute flea."
    },
    {
      "start": 275.36,
      "end": 276.16,
      "text": "아주 재미있는"
    },
    {
      "start": 276.16,
      "end": 277.72,
      "text": "시나리오를 펼쳐가는"
    },
    {
      "start": 277.72,
      "end": 278.78,
      "text": "순간이었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 279.42,
      "end": 280.1,
      "text": "근데 그들이"
    },
    {
      "start": 280.1,
      "end": 280.86,
      "text": "잘하는 것들이"
    },
    {
      "start": 280.86,
      "end": 281.5,
      "text": "무엇인지"
    },
    {
      "start": 281.5,
      "end": 282.7,
      "text": "아까 들으셨을 텐데"
    },
    {
      "start": 282.7,
      "end": 284.24,
      "text": "라울 같은 경우에는"
    },
    {
      "start": 284.24,
      "end": 285.32,
      "text": "배달을 잘하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 285.32,
      "end": 287.0,
      "text": "에밀 같은 경우에는"
    },
    {
      "start": 287.0,
      "end": 287.62,
      "text": "영화,"
    },
    {
      "start": 288.04,
      "end": 288.26,
      "text": "그 다음에"
    },
    {
      "start": 288.26,
      "end": 288.92,
      "text": "루시일은"
    },
    {
      "start": 288.92,
      "end": 289.94,
      "text": "공연을 잘한다"
    },
    {
      "start": 289.94,
      "end": 291.02,
      "text": "라는 장점들을"
    },
    {
      "start": 291.02,
      "end": 291.6,
      "text": "살짝살짝"
    },
    {
      "start": 291.6,
      "end": 292.42,
      "text": "들어봤습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 293.24,
      "end": 294.2,
      "text": "일단 주요 표현들"
    },
    {
      "start": 294.2,
      "end": 294.84,
      "text": "알려주세요."
    },
    {
      "start": 294.84,
      "end": 296.3,
      "text": "Shrink him down"
    },
    {
      "start": 296.3,
      "end": 297.8,
      "text": "Shrink him down"
    },
    {
      "start": 297.8,
      "end": 298.56,
      "text": "Shrink"
    },
    {
      "start": 298.56,
      "end": 299.36,
      "text": "들으셨죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 299.58,
