      "start": 602.68,
      "end": 604.02,
      "text": "여기까지 들으셨어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 604.02,
      "end": 607.66,
      "text": "너는 공연 분야에서 전문가야"
    },
    {
      "start": 607.66,
      "end": 608.6,
      "text": "But you know"
    },
    {
      "start": 608.6,
      "end": 609.06,
      "text": "하지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 609.06,
      "end": 611.46,
      "text": "You know what"
    },
    {
      "start": 611.46,
      "end": 612.58,
      "text": "뭐 한다고"
    },
    {
      "start": 612.58,
      "end": 614.5,
      "text": "네, 뒷부분에 아주 끊겼어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 614.5,
      "end": 615.76,
      "text": "Exactly"
    },
    {
      "start": 615.76,
      "end": 616.84,
      "text": "네, 여기에서"
    },
    {
      "start": 616.84,
      "end": 618.02,
      "text": "Lucille이 치고 들어옵니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 618.02,
      "end": 618.6,
      "text": "Exactly"
    },
    {
      "start": 618.6,
      "end": 620.06,
      "text": "바로 그거야"
    },
    {
      "start": 620.06,
      "end": 621.26,
      "text": "정확해"
    },
    {
      "start": 621.26,
      "end": 622.66,
      "text": "라고 치고 들어왔어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 622.66,
      "end": 623.74,
      "text": "그게 뭐예요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 623.92,
      "end": 624.36,
      "text": "그러니까요"
    },
    {
      "start": 624.36,
      "end": 624.94,
      "text": "애매한데요"
    },
    {
      "start": 624.94,
      "end": 626.42,
      "text": "애매모호하게 이렇게 얘기하네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 626.42,
      "end": 627.98,
      "text": "마치 암호처럼"
    },
    {
      "start": 627.98,
      "end": 629.58,
      "text": "이야기를 해주고 있는 장면입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 629.58,
      "end": 630.96,
      "text": "이제 구체적으로"
    },
    {
      "start": 630.96,
      "end": 632.64,
      "text": "이들이 어떻게 진행을 할지"
    },
    {
      "start": 632.64,
      "end": 634.24,
      "text": "두고 봐야 되는 순간이네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 634.24,
      "end": 635.7,
      "text": "아, remember Lucille?"
    },
    {
      "start": 635.84,
      "end": 637.9,
      "text": "She has a performance coming up"
    },
    {
      "start": 637.9,
      "end": 638.36,
      "text": "Right"
    },
    {
      "start": 638.36,
      "end": 640.38,
      "text": "A performance with the commissioner"
    },
    {
      "start": 640.38,
      "end": 642.3,
      "text": "Maybe they're going to use"
    },
    {
      "start": 642.3,
      "end": 643.7,
      "text": "her show business skills"
    },
    {
      "start": 643.7,
      "end": 645.94,
      "text": "to make a plan"
    },
    {
      "start": 645.94,
      "end": 647.36,
      "text": "to save the little flea"
    },
    {
      "start": 647.36,
      "end": 650.24,
      "text": "이렇게 예측을 할 수 있게 해주셨네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 650.24,
      "end": 651.44,
      "text": "네, 이 부분"
    },
    {
      "start": 651.44,
      "end": 653.1,
      "text": "마지막으로 한 번 더 들어보겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 653.1,
      "end": 655.35,
      "text": "If only we could shrink him down"
    },
    {
      "start": 655.35,
      "end": 656.55,
      "text": "to his normal size"
    },
    {
      "start": 656.55,
      "end": 658.01,
      "text": "then no one would ever find him"
    },
    {
      "start": 658.01,
      "end": 658.81,
      "text": "Smaller you are"
    },
    {
      "start": 658.81,
      "end": 659.79,
      "text": "the less people look at you"
    },
    {
      "start": 659.79,
      "end": 661.79,
      "text": "At least that's been my experience"
    },
    {
      "start": 661.79,
      "end": 663.05,
      "text": "There's only one person"
    },
    {
      "start": 663.05,
      "end": 664.01,
      "text": "who could save Franco"
    },
    {
      "start": 664.01,
      "end": 665.79,
      "text": "and he's in New York right now"
    },
    {
      "start": 665.79,
      "end": 667.81,
      "text": "But we don't need him"
    },
    {
      "start": 667.81,
      "end": 668.93,
      "text": "Lucille"
    },
    {
      "start": 668.93,
      "end": 670.35,
      "text": "No offense"
    },
    {
      "start": 670.35,
      "end": 672.49,
      "text": "We're talking big-time science here, okay?"
    },
    {
      "start": 672.63,
      "end": 673.65,
      "text": "All I know is deliveries"
    },
    {
      "start": 673.65,
      "end": 675.11,
      "text": "Emile's all about movies"
    },
    {
      "start": 675.11,
      "end": 676.57,
      "text": "You're an expert in show business"
    },
    {
      "start": 676.57,
      "end": 677.07,
      "text": "but, you know"
    },
    {
      "start": 677.07,
      "end": 677.65,
      "text": "Exactly"
    },
    {
      "start": 677.65,
      "end": 680.73,
      "text": "네, 이 종자님께서"
    },
    {
      "start": 680.73,
      "end": 681.95,
      "text": "Thanks a lot"
    },
    {
      "start": 681.95,
      "end": 683.19,
      "text": "Have a happy day"
    },
    {
      "start": 683.19,
      "end": 687.03,
      "text": "You too have a wonderful, happy, beautiful, happy day"
    },
    {
      "start": 687.03,
      "end": 688.95,
      "text": "Happy 두 번 썼네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 688.95,
      "end": 690.93,
      "text": "네, 무슨 랩을 하시는 줄 알았어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 690.93,
      "end": 692.85,
      "text": "오늘 기분 좋게 여기에서"
    },
    {
      "start": 692.85,
      "end": 694.07,
      "text": "마무리해보도록 할게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 694.07,
      "end": 695.21,
      "text": "우리는 see you tomorrow"
    },
    {
      "start": 695.21,
      "end": 696.31,
      "text": "I'll see you then"
    }
  ]
}